To check that `foo` satisfies its contract, we compile, instrument and analyse the program as follows:

```sh
goto-cc fptr.c
goto-instrument \
--restrict-function-pointer foo.CALL/arr_fun_contract \
--dfcc main \
--enforce-contract foo \
a.out b.out
cbmc b.out
```

